1.com/社會新聞/295189/公營骨灰龕位設20年期-無續期骨灰以綠色殯葬處理\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F295189%2F%E5%85%AC%E7%87%9F%E9%AA%A8%E7%81%B0%E9%BE%95%E4%BD%8D%E8%A8%AD20%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%9F-%E7%84%A1%E7%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F%E9%AA%A8%E7%81%B0%E4%BB%A5%E7%B6%A0%E8%89%B2%E6%AE%AF%E8%91%AC%E8%99%95%E7%90%86&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=21bd9e45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/295189/公營骨灰龕位設20年期-無續期骨灰以綠色殯葬處理</a>"},{"pid":"6e3d2716c5209133c5f8fbdfc3709813e6620e3b","tid":1059252,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"東華三院校董四分一價<br />\n東華三院校長半價<br />\n東華三院老師兩倍價"},{"pid":"82ab39c3f7d72b9832f9ac81a552013122757f9d","tid":1059252,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:00:23.000Z","msg":"去西伯利亞天葬算了"},{"pid":"5a7982e174f2150b9e1f05a451a929993f59d615","tid":1059252,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6cdfbdba83ef6b94b7502a594ae8938cce48dd4","tid":1059252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12f42ba0e7a006099d9a7a1cdb537af560b34211","tid":1059252,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好死住囉<br />\n點解唔努力D打多幾份工 搵多幾個錢先死呢？<br />\n唔好怨天尤人啦 香港人要有獅子山精神"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"獅子山精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/FXYOPZk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXYOPZk.gif&h=4501ba6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"奶波魔魔召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f8c2cf1ce15347c3b28b2f693d0c86525d9330","tid":1059252,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:24:34.000Z